m(s) in the Design and\r\nConstruction supervision of similar nature and\r\ncomplex project in the last 10 (ten) years; \r\n\r\nThe \'similar nature and complexity\' is defined as multi-spam\r\nPre-stressed concrete/composite Box Girder Bridges built\r\nunder Plant & Design-Build Contract on river channel with\r\nthe following properties:\r\ni) Length of bridge: Not less than 1,000 (one thousand meters)\r\nwith spans of 90 meters; and\r\nii) Large diameter (more than 1.5 meters) deep (more than 80\r\nmeters) pile foundation.', NULL, 1, 1, 1, '2020-07-06 21:40:27', '2020-08-19 18:58:41'),
